Examples of customer reviews that were submitted directly to our website from our website’s users (with corresponding date and username), include:
4/4/2008: “"As a video production company owner/operator for 15 years, I have dealt with a large number of tape/media suppliers. I usually shop by price, but service matters too. I received BOTH from TapeOnline and more. I easily found the product on their site and the specific amount I needed, the prices were very good, and processing was easy. I received excellent follow-up communication, and the items arrived quickly by FedEx, nicely packaged with no damage. It was a pleasant suprise to find a package of candy inside the box too. Compared to many of the other online media companies I have dealt with in the past, and some of the service nightmares, TapeOnline is head and shoulders above the rest! True quality customer service!"” –vcoaster
http://www.resellerratings.com/store/view/TapeOnline_Electric_Picture_Company_Inc/page/15
